docs.abstract: Growth in the number of low-cost trans-Atlantic flights and a willingness by airlines to undercut rivals have led to cheap tickets to Europe.

docs.lead_paragraph: Forget Yellowstone. Right now, you can buy a ticket to travel from New York to Paris in August — on a major American airline — for under $500.

docs.abstract: Hotels are starting to rent out private homes. But there’s one big difference from Airbnb — the hotels’ private lodgings come with hotel-like services.
docs.snippet: Hotels are starting to rent out private homes. But there’s one big difference from Airbnb — the hotels’ private lodgings come with hotel-like services.
docs.lead_paragraph: Hotels largely stood by as home sharing companies like Airbnb began offering travelers a chance to bypass a standardized hotel room and, instead, live like a local.

headline.main: Blurring Lines, Hotels Get Into the Home-Sharing Business
headline.print_headline: Sharing a Home, but With All the Comforts of a Hotel Room

docs.abstract: The hype of tax holidays, one tax expert says, is out of proportion to the savings offered to shoppers. Plus, some retailers may raise prices as shoppers rush in.
docs.snippet: The hype of tax holidays, one tax expert says, is out of proportion to the savings offered to shoppers. Plus, some retailers may raise prices as shoppers rush in.
docs.lead_paragraph: As summer vacation nears an end, some states are holding the annual back-to-school ritual known as the sales tax holiday. But some tax experts said shoppers should be realistic about how much they will be saving.

docs.abstract: If your friends are getting email messages you didn’t send, someone may be forging your address on spammy activities.
docs.snippet: If your friends are getting email messages you didn’t send, someone may be forging your address on spammy activities.
docs.lead_paragraph: Q. I received one (and only one) warning from a friend that she had gotten a “this might be of interest” email from me and said I was hacked. Nobody else I have asked got it. Is there a way to verify I have been hacked before I go through the trouble of changing my primary email address?

headline.main: How to Look for Proof of a Spoof
